    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it does show its age. The engine runs well, but you can expect some minor oil seepage and a suspension that feels a bit soft compared to a newer model. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some fading on the dashboard. It is a solid, functional car that would benefit from some cosmetic TLC and a routine tune-up.",
