    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 Luxury AWD Touring Edition in a stunning Deep Baltic Blue. This vehicle has been a reliable daily driver and remains in solid mechanical health. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, superficial scratch near the rear wheel well\u2014typical for a car of this age but nothing that detracts from its overall presence. Inside, the cabin features premium pebble-grain leather seating that has been treated regularly; there are no tears or heavy bolsters wear, though the driver\u2019s seat shows light natural creasing. All electronic features, including the panoramic sunroof, dual-zone climate control, and the upgraded infotainment system, are fully functional. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises. I have kept a strict maintenance schedule, including a recent oil change and a fresh set of brake pads installed last month. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining. This is a dependable, well-cared-for vehicle that offers a premium driving experience without the new-car price tag. Clean title in hand.",
